{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20260428/s00005/8b888be7872443cbac62c54aa24b4da9.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:1em\">\n    <p>韓國前總統尹錫悅的妻子金建希涉嫌操縱股價、收受賄賂等罪行一案今天（28日）二審宣判，判囚4年。今年1月時一審宣判金建希判處20個月監禁。（韓聯社/新華社）</p>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-28T14:33:06.671780+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":77,"images":1,"source":"明報 國際","fallback":"none"}}